ji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有錢就裝埋鏡頭</blockquote><br />\n又SENSOR又鏡頭好似好重覆咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13598cd400a4840071c8e1f10ed3cbf67957fad9","tid":58762,"uid":20602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:43:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原裝有晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n窮撚渣2手車 , 高年份 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e23c1e10a6106c995f2acea4cda5b62ee5beef28","tid":58762,"uid":70689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T07:53:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>換左架車, 上手冇留低個cam又冇裝sensor, 諗緊裝邊個好。用開sensor, 朋友話用cam 有好多死角 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家用咩多?</blockquote><br />\n車兩樣都有<br />\n你如果是旦揀一樣就泊車cam"},{"pid":"7fb4f9354b35fa6b286f2ee5b6c8871f79317401","tid":58762,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T08:07:52.000Z","msg":"一定係車cam, 所謂死角睇鏡就夠<br />\n貨車都同16座都係用cam, 唔係sensor"},{"pid":"dbc37b812f636fbca5799b75938350bb67a6945e","tid":58762,"uid":37195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T08:22:19.000Z","msg":"是但一樣已經夠，泊車係睇鏡，呢兩樣野係用黎防盲點（即係有條撚屌細路企係你車尾又矮過你後窗）<br />\n<br />\n利申兩樣有哂"},{"pid":"0a2257e1fdaf702337e0a332ff7895155043999b","tid":58762,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T08:23:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"952de17fc34f74900c4dab4858ffc9c14571fbac","tid":58762,"uid":23763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T09:08:12.000Z","msg":"Why not both"},{"pid":"fca91b608c158797fc0802ffd6845f9bab2569da","tid":58762,"uid":43833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T12:47:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>乜都無用，直接伸個頭出窗睇<img src=\"/assets/